title: Fredrika's Fountain
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Buffet, Salad bar, Finnish
description: Cafeteria and restaurant serving lunch til 14.30 with coffee, tea, and baked goods (some vegan) all day. Lunch is vegan soup, salad, bread, and hummus. Fredrika's Fountain is an old pleasant wooden house 10-minute walk from centre. Features rotating art exhibition on its walls. There is also a little organic food shop, yoga centre, and natural treatment rooms.
